        <Parent_String>Massim Area sculptural styles [300264758], Massim Area [300021887], Papua New Guinea regional styles [300264809], Papua New Guinean [300386489], Melanesian [300021867], Oceanic [300021854], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
